Welcome to Hubmind

ğŸ§±Â Powerful Blocks

There are 92 well designed and heavily functional blocks from theÂ TailblocksÂ project.


ğŸÂ Assets Uploading

Stores the images uploaded in the editor in your repo. Displays them when needed on production.


ğŸƒÂ Delightful Builder

Powered byÂ Grapes.js, a flexible and feature-full editor with CSS like options similar to Webflow.


ğŸ•¹Â Data Ownership

Destack stores all your assets on Github, Bitbucket etc through the editor. There are no external dependencies to manage or worry about.


ğŸ‘©ğŸ»â€ğŸ’»Â Developer Ready

Works out of the box with anyÂ Next.jsÂ project. Build a few landing pages with Destack and the rest of your app with the usuall Next.js toolkit.


ğŸƒğŸ½Â Instant Deployment

Destack supports environment detection. The visual editor comes up only in development and the compiled version on production.


ğŸ“¸Â Easy Setup

Click theÂ DeployÂ button below to create a new Destack project on Vercel or head toÂ Installing the pluginÂ for instructions for your existing Next.js projects.
